			(symbol "MasterSoftware_1_1"
				(text "Data from slaves:\n min/max/average/total voltage per module\n min/max/average temperature per module\n voltage/temperature faults\nCommands to slaves:\n Begin cell balancing\n Alter all settings\n Emergency discharge (multi-command?)\nProcess data:\n min/max/average/total pack voltage\n  - optional sensor to read full pack voltage, compare to calculated\n min/max/average pack temperature\n\nDrive mode:\n DriveEn present\n No hard voltage/temperature faults\n Command vehicle to reduce limits if soft voltage/temperature fault\n Handle precharge and contactor closing\n  - Enable precharge and HV- (option to switch to HV+)\n  - When external message and total pack voltage are within\n       threshold, close remaining contactor.\n Allow for bidirectional flow\n\nCharge mode:\n ChargeEn present\n No hard voltage/temperature faults\n Handle precharge and contactor closing\n  - Enable precharge and HV- (option to switch to HV+)\n  - When external message and total pack voltage are within\n       threshold, close remaining contactor.\n Once contactor cycling is complete, allow for charge only.\n\nDisplay:\n Direct control of simple display or communication to display circuit.\n Display individual/total cell data\n User selectable or external commands\n\nAllow vehicle to unlock and change all settings in master and slaves."
					(at 0.254 -39.37 0)
					(effects
						(font
							(size 1.27 1.27)
						)
						(justify left)
					)
				)
